    "draft": false,
    "content": "### Grab a bite before your flight\n\nDiscover the restaurants, cafes and bars that MBIA has to offer. Grab a quick bite or settle down for a relaxing meal before or after your flight.\n\n## Before Security\n\n### Rituals Coffee House\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 423-2801 (473) 534-5115\n\n**✉️ Email**\n\nteam@effilution.com\n\n### Skyline Café\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 535 – 9358\n\n### First & Last Bar & Bites\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n1 (473) 415 – 0488\n\n### Ants Nest Restaurant\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 457 ANTS (2687)\n\n**✉️ Email**\n\nantsnestgrenada@gmail.com\n\n### After Security\n\n### ☕Spice Isle Coffee\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 232-3000\n\n### 🍽️ First Class Restaurant\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 405-1088\n\n### Sky Sport\n\n**📞 Telephone**\n\n(473) 405-1088",
