    "draft": false,
    "content": "### Advertise With Us\n\nAt MBIA, our top priority is expanding and enhancing air service offerings to meet the growing demand of our vibrant population and thriving tourism sector. We are committed to creating new opportunities for airlines to connect Grenada with the world.\n\n## Indoor Advertising Opportunities\n\nIndoor advertising at MBIA is proudly managed by RG Media, offering tailored solutions designed to maximize brand visibility. From strategic placements to customized campaigns, RG Media helps businesses connect with travelers and elevate their presence within Grenada’s busiest gateways.\n\n### Contact Information\n\n**RG Media LLC** **Address:** 2760 Fringe Lane Easton, PA 18040-6206 USA **Email:** [enquires@rg.media](mailto:enquires@rg.media) [gil@rg.media](mailto:gil@rg.media)\n\n## Outdoor Advertising Opportunities\n\nOutdoor advertising at MBIA is expertly managed by Pipeline Promotions, offering customized solutions to maximize your brand’s visibility. From high-traffic locations to impactful designs, Pipeline Promotions ensures your message reaches travelers and creates lasting impressions.\n\n### Contact Information\n\n**Pipeline Promotions** **Telephone:** 1 (473)-538-7911 **Email:** [pipeline.gnd@gmail.com](mailto:pipeline.gnd@gmail.com) [pipelinepromos@gmail.com](mailto:pipelinepromos@gmail.com)\n\n## Pop-Up Booths & Promotional Counters\n\nTake advantage of unique opportunities to showcase your brand at Maurice Bishop International Airport through pop-up booths or promotional counters. Whether for retail sales or brand awareness campaigns, these high-visibility spaces connect you directly with travelers.\n\nTo learn more about how your business can benefit from an airport pop-up, contact the BDCC Department.\n\n### Contact Information\n\n**Grenada Airports Authority** Business Development & Corporate Communications (BDCC) Department **Email:** [bdcc@gaa.gd](mailto:bdcc@gaa.gd) **Telephone:** 1 (473) 444-4101 ext 2516\n\n- GAA\n- MBIA\n- Lauriston Airport\n\n#### At The Airport\n\n- Car Rental\n- Customs Information\n- Duty-Free Shops\n- Executive Lounge\n\n#### Useful Links\n\n- Board of Directors\n- Management Team\n- FAQ’s\n- Careers & Opportunities\n\n## Newsletter",
