    "title": "Aeronautical Fees",
    "dek": "The GAA's schedule of aeronautical fees and charges for aircraft operators at Maurice Bishop International Airport and Lauriston Airport.",
    "section": "business",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "The Grenada Airports Authority publishes its schedule of aeronautical fees and\ncharges for all aircraft operations at Maurice Bishop International Airport\n(GND) and Lauriston Airport (CRU), including landing, parking, navigation and\npassenger service charges.\n\n## Current schedule\n\n- [Schedule of Fees and Charges — Aeronautical (updated December 2023)](/documents/SCHEDULE-OF-FEES-AND-CHARGES-AERONAUTICA-L-Updated-Dec-2023.pdf) (PDF, 8 pages)\n\nFor queries about aeronautical charges, invoicing or operator accounts, please\n[contact the Authority](/contact).",
