    "title": "Leadership & Governance",
    "dek": "Meet our leadership team—the driving force behind our vision and success. With diverse expertise and a shared commitment to innovation and excellence, they l…",
    "section": "corporate",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "### Meet the leaders who shape our vision\n\nMeet our leadership team—the driving force behind our vision and success. With diverse expertise and a shared commitment to innovation and excellence, they lead the organization in delivering exceptional results while fostering a culture of collaboration and growth. Guided by strategic insight and forward-thinking leadership, this team ensures we stay ahead of industry trends and continue shaping the future of aviation.\n\n### MINISTRY OF CIVIL AVIATION\n\n## Hon. Dickon A. T. Mitchell\n\nMinister of Civil Aviation Ministry of Infrastructure, Public Utilities, Civil Aviation and Transportation\n\n## Mr. Marlon Carter\n\nCivil Aviation Officer Ministry of Infrastructure, Public Utilities, Civil Aviation and Transportation\n\n### BOARD OF DIRECTORS / BOARD MEMBERS\n\nGAA’s Board of Directors is composed of seasoned business professionals whose diverse backgrounds and extensive experience provide strong governance and strategic direction for the Authority. Working closely with the Executive Management team, the Board plays a critical role in shaping the airport’s future and its impact on the island and the wider region.\n\nThe Board consists of ten directors with expertise across various sectors. They are responsible for setting policy and overseeing the general administration of the Authority’s affairs, ensuring operational excellence and long-term growth.\n\n## Ms. Shonda Cadore\n\nChairwoman\n\n## Mr. Sydney Charles\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Zaid Rahaman\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Mahendra Singh\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Jeanette Dabreo\n\nBoard Secretary\n\n## Mr. Jeanette Dabreo\n\nBoard Secretary\n\n## Mr. Nigel Noel\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Sylvester Quarless\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Kerry Pierre\n\nDirector\n\n## Mr. Stephen Campbell\n\nDirector\n\n### MANAGEMENT TEAM/ EXECUTIVE MANAGERS\n\nOur leadership team is committed to taking MBIA to new heights every day. At the heart of our success is a group of dedicated professionals whose knowledge, passion, and commitment ensure that every guest enjoys a safe and seamless experience.\n\nThe Management Team consists of department managers responsible for the day-to-day operations of the Authority. This team is led by the General Manager/Chief Executive Officer, who is accountable to the Board of Directors for implementing policies and driving strategic goals.\n\n## Mr. Edgar Stephen\n\nChief Executive Officer\n\n## Mrs. Cristina Joseph\n\nDirector of Operations\n\n## Mr. Kurt Williams\n\nManager of Information Systems & Digitalisation Services\n\n## Ms. Asha Francis\n\nFinance Manager\n\n## Mrs. Jamilla Linton – Anane\n\nDirector of Human Resources\n\n## Mrs. Tuwana Lendor-Slinger\n\nBDCC Manager\n\n## Mr. Gerard Tamar\n\nManager of Meteorology\n\n## Mr. Glen Forsyth\n\nMaintenance Manager\n\n## Mr. Dennis Philbert\n\nManager of Air Traffic Control\n\n## Mr. Emon Charles\n\nManager of Security\n\n## Mrs. Kim McQuilkin\n\nOSHE Manager\n\n## Ms. Cecil Mitchell\n\nQAC Manager\n\n## Mr. Adrian Panchoo\n\nOfficer in Charge - CFR\n\n## David Andrew\n\nOfficer in Charge – Lauriston Airport\n\n- GAA\n- MBIA\n- Lauriston Airport\n\n#### At The Airport\n\n- Car Rental\n- Customs Information\n- Duty-Free Shops\n- Executive Lounge\n\n#### Useful Links\n\n- Board of Directors\n- Management Team\n- FAQ’s\n- Careers & Opportunities\n\n## Newsletter",
