    "title": "Our Partners",
    "dek": "Driving success through smart partnerships",
    "section": "corporate",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "### Driving success through smart partnerships\n\nWe collaborate with local, regional, and international partners and stakeholders to deliver world-class experiences for the thousands of passengers who pass through our terminal each year. Together, we build global connections that elevate every journey.\n\n### Government Agencies\n\n✈[Government of Grenada](https://www.gov.gd/) ✈Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Trade & Export Development ✈RGPF Drug Squad ✈[Immigration & Passport Control](https://www.gov.gd/index.php/documents/immigration) ✈[Grenada Customs & Excise Division](http://www.grenadacustoms.com/) ✈[Ministry of Agriculture](https://www.gov.gd/agriculture/) ✈[National Disaster Management Agency (NaDMA)](https://www.nadma.gd/)\n\n### Tourism\n\n✈[Caribbean Tourism Organization (CTO)](https://www.onecaribbean.org/) ✈[Grenada Tourism Authority (GTA)](https://www.puregrenada.com/) ✈[Grenada Hotel & Tourism Authority (GHTA)](https://ghta.org/) ✈[Caribbean Hotel & Tourism Association (CHTA)](https://caribbeanhotelandtourism.com/) ✈[Spicemas Corporation (SMC)](https://spicemasgrenada.com/)\n\n### Trade & Investment\n\n✈[Investment Migration Agency (IMA) Grenada](https://imagrenada.gd/) ✈[Grenada Investment Development Corporation (GIDC)](https://gidc.gd/)\n\n### Regulatory Bodies\n\n✈[Eastern Caribbean Civil Aviation Authority (ECCAA)](https://www.eccaa.aero/) ✈[International Air Transport Association (IATA)](https://www.iata.org/) ✈[Transportation Security Administration (TSA)](https://www.tsa.gov/) ✈[International Civil Aviation Organization (ICAO)](https://www.icao.int/) ✈[Federal Aviation Administration (FAA)](https://www.faa.gov/)\n\n### Health Organizations\n\n✈[World Health Organization (WHO)](https://www.who.int/) ✈[Pan American Health Organization (PAHO)](https://www.paho.org/en)\n\n### Training & Certification\n\n✈[Airports Council International (ACI-LAC)](https://aci-lac.aero/en/home/) ✈[Caribbean Institute for Meteorology and Hydrology (CIMH)](https://www.cimh.edu.bb/) ✈[Civil Aviation Training Centre (CATC)](https://caa.gov.tt/civil-aviation-training-centre/)\n\n### Airlines\n\n✈[American Airlines](https://www.aa.com) ✈[JetBlue Airways](https://www.jetblue.com) ✈[Delta Air Lines](https://www.delta.com) ✈[Air Canada](https://www.aircanada.com) ✈[WestJet](https://www.westjet.com) ✈[Caribbean Airlines](https://www.caribbean-airlines.com) ✈[InterCaribbean Airways](https://www.intercaribbean.com/) ✈[SVG Air](https://flysvgair.com/) ✈[LIAT Air](https://www.flyliatair.com/) ✈[Sunrise Airways](https://www.sunriseairways.net) ✈[British Airways](https://www.britishairways.com) ✈[Virgin Atlantic](https://www.virginatlantic.com)",
