    "section": "corporate",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "### Caring for the environment and local communities Connecting communities. Preserving our planet. Working towards a sustainable future Building a more sustainable future.\n\nAt Maurice Bishop International Airport (MBIA), we are committed to reducing our environmental footprint while being a good neighbor to the communities we serve. Our mission is to uncover ways—big and small—to leave a better world for future generations. By combining environmental stewardship with community engagement, we strive to create meaningful change. Discover how we’re making a difference. Learn more about the initiatives we have in place to support this mission below.\n\nSustainability & Community\n\n## Sustainability at GAA\n\nAt Maurice Bishop International Airport (MBIA), we are committed to reducing our environmental footprint and acting as responsible stewards of the planet.\n\nExplore Sustainability Initiatives →\n\nSustainability & Community\n\n## Community Engagement\n\nAt Maurice Bishop International Airport (MBIA), we are committed to reducing our environmental footprint and acting as responsible stewards of the planet.\n\nExplore Community Initiatives →",
